Error: Error: "Server Unable To Connect To Database" 

Step-By-Step

Solution: 1. Go to your Pterodactyl panel and login to your account.
2. Navigate to "Servers" and click on  the server which is facing this issue.
3. Click on "Database" tab and verify the database host, database name, database user and password are correctly entered.
